          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Low"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure is straightforward, involving a simple query with a few joins and conditional logic to set an output parameter. It does not involve complex operations, transactions, or error handling, which keeps its complexity low."
        }
      ]
    },
